Looney Tunes Showcase: Volume 1 is a Blu-ray disc announced by Warner Home Video. It was released on January 10, 2012. It contains 25 Looney Tunes and Merrie Melodies and numerous supplements. It is a separate release of Disc 1 of the Looney Tunes Platinum Collection: Volume 1. This will be the series for Looney Tunes and Merrie Melodies cartoons in standard Blu-ray cases. But due to low budgets in remastering the shorts, The Looney Tunes Showcase was discontinued.
